AbstractObjective<T extends org.spongepowered.api.event.Event> - Class in com.atherys.quests.api.objective
An abstract implementation of Objective which checks whether or not the Objective's event corresponds to the event being supplied via AbstractObjective.notify(Event, Quester).
This is the preferred method for introducing new Objectives, as any such would require code of this sort to filter out irrelevant events.
